node.text:
German luxury RV specialist @volkner.mobil has released its most expensive motor home to date. The Volkner Performance S sees an L-shaped kitchen, a master suite, a full-width bathroom, a 2,000-watt solar array, a wine locker, and a Burmester sound system that costs $355,000 USD alone. Adding to the $7.7 million price tag is a @bugatti Chiron stowed in a slide-out garage.
